name: Purple/Black Loud Pack "The Nose Knows" T-Shirt
description:
This is a classic custom t-shirt. The straight-cut men's t-shirt is made of pre-shrunk and ring-spun cotton.
It is a star personalized t-shirt, comfortable and stylish. Its high quality and fashioning shows in terms of
double-thread seems on its cuffs and hem as well as its double-beveled collar edges (1X1 ribbing). A collar
neckband makes for a comfortable fit. Fabric weight 190g/sqm. 100% cotton.

name: Pink/Black Loud Pack "The Nose Knows" Hoody
description: The custom hoody is cut straight and is slightly fit to the body. You'll be warm and ready for outdoor fun in this stylish men's hoody. It features pronounced sleeve cuffs as well as a prominent waistband hem and kangaroo pocket fringes. Thanks to its high 320g/sqm consistency and its polyester fraction it will always fit after washing. 80% cotton, 20% polyester.
